Detects whether the current or the given namespace has subpages enabled. Returns "yes" if it does, and an empty string otherwise.

This template can be substituted.

=== Usage ===
* {{tlx|ns has subpages}} → {{ns has subpages}}
* {{tlx|ns has subpages|Template}} → {{ns has subpages|Template}}
* {{tlx|ns has subpages|Category}} → {{ns has subpages|Category}}
* {{tlx|ns has subpages|<nowiki></nowiki>}} <small>(''main space'')</small> → {{ns has subpages|}}
* {{tlx|ns has subpages|<nowiki>{{ns:0}}</nowiki>}} <small>(''main space'')</small> → {{ns has subpages|{{ns:0}}}}
* {{tlx|ns has subpages|:}} <small>(''main space'')</small> → {{ns has subpages|:}}
* {{tlx|ns has subpages|<nowiki>{{ns:Talk}}</nowiki>}} → {{ns has subpages|{{ns:Talk}}}}

